	<div class="container content">
		<p>
			<span>This is AccuPay</span>, an AccuLynx Mobile Payment application for
			collecting secure online payments at the job location. The main
			requirement for the application was the inclusion of ACH and Credit Card
			processing. These additions needed to worked seamlessly with the desktop
			application by automatically updating the job information and notifying
			any required users of the completed transaction.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="container content">
		<h3>We Started with Research:</h3>
		<p>
			We first developed some questions we needed answers to understand the
			user's needs for this product feature:
		</p>
		<p>
			Who will use the AccuPay app? Why? What tasks needed to be completed? What
			features do the users want?
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="container content">
		<h3>What did we find out?</h3>
	</div>
	<div class="quote-wrapper">
		<blockquote class="quote-card yellow-card">
			<p>
				It takes too much time to go back and make calls and send reminders to
				collect payment.
			</p>

			<cite> - Doug, the persona </cite>
		</blockquote>
	</div>

	<div class="container content">
		<h3>The Persona</h3>
	</div>

	<img
