		<h3>An Interesting note:</h3>
		<p>
			After testing the user flow with a few of our AccuLynx customers, we
			needed to make a few tweaks to allow the user to enter the card details
			manually. The business initially thought the user would not want to
			manually enter the ACH payments because of the higher processing fees.
		</p>
		<p>
			The application needed to allow the user to collect a payment quickly and
			email a receipt after processing. The application needed to be simple and
			intuitive for our users.. I looked at other designs for inspiration and
			sorted out what worked to fit the desired outcome.
		</p>
